        <a href="https://www.douban.com/people/aixiaoke/" class="name">艾小柯</a>

            <span class="allstar50 main-title-rating" title="力荐"></span>

        <span content="2010-03-30" class="main-meta">2010-03-30 09:56:09</span>


            <span class="publisher right">
                <a class="publisher" target="_blank" href="https://book.douban.com/subject/1017143/">上海译文出版社2003版</a>
